	<p>What this really comes down to is that poor people lack the drive that the successful rich people have and they want to bring the successful people down because they can't hack it.  Instead of bitching about the rich making money, why don't you get off your ass and get a better paying job?  If you can't get educated so you can.  And don't tell me you still can't because it's a lie.  <br />
<br />
Now, I'm far from rich and I've always been far from it.  Throughout my life, my father has supported us until about 4 years ago when my mother got a steady job she loved...until 4 years ago, my father supported a family of 5 with $35,000 a year and now with my mother's income, the household income is about $55,000.  I've promised my parents that I will take care of them because, unlike so many people, I actually have big dreams of making loads of money and the dream will turn into reality because I have the drive, unlike most people.</p>
	
	
	
